# lpm-custom
Custom hooks for lfs-pkmg

Directories:

--------------------------------------------------------------------
batch

File list of build and/or group files.



--------------------------------------------------------------------
build

Build scripts for non-book packages.


--------------------------------------------------------------------
list

Pre- and post- install hook scripts for lpm install lists.


--------------------------------------------------------------------
group

File list of book packages.


--------------------------------------------------------------------
meta

File list of batch files.


--------------------------------------------------------------------
script

Script hooks for modification of the lpm build files.


--------------------------------------------------------------------
package

Pre- and post- install hook scripts for lpm packages.

